{"tid":1796914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[獨派面對現實] 獨立左既香港, 對美國黎講係零價值, 美國會唔會出兵幫本身有價值既香港變成零價值?","createTime":"2019-12-25T03:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T12:17:34.000Z","uid":31637,"like":25,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"49f7f636019e295e734fc21269e8c286dbd73208","tid":1796914,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"你要外國勢力幫你, 你都要向外國勢力展示你有被幫既價值<br />\n好撚明顯獨立後既香港對外國勢力黎講係零價值, 垃圾黎, 因為好多野只可以係一國二制既情況之下先做到, 獨立左既香港係完全做唔撚到<br />\n咁你仲幻想會有外國勢力會出兵同你班友一齊打獨立戰爭?<br />\n要分裂中國既籌碼美國已經到手, 果個就係台灣<br />\n唔需要再多一個, 好撚明顯美國就係想香港有普選多過獨立"},{"pid":"447fc37d72f7c3f6935585709fe4b3a2450e7b97","tid":1796914,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T03:58:16.000Z","msg":"借個位嚟推廣連儂廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解愈嚟愈少和理非出？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1796473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1796473</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c44cf98c1ed864f3896d02c8557e14b8971479d5","tid":1796914,"uid":5205,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:00:02.000Z","msg":"可以用脫離中國 繼續做中轉站"},{"pid":"25192375fc63662126d66a48e16cb6ab8bf69022","tid":1796914,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:00:56.000Z","msg":"要歸英先"},{"pid":"bdfda40db81554ff8d386f0734d2c2064cce3437","tid":1796914,"uid":69334,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:01:04.000Z","msg":"反獨派，拉<br />\n<br />\n係鍾意日日提住港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港獨立 唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32cb879ce798f9d97df765e904d578e7b362d9e","tid":1796914,"uid":4618,"like":21,"